                                        <p>
                                            <h2 class='center'>!{activationCode}</h2>
                                        </p>
                                        <p>
                                            |If you closed your browser use this link: <a href="https://protect.ixt.global/activate?activationCode=!{activationCode}">https://protect.ixt.global/activate?activationCode=!{activationCode}</a>
                                        </p>
                                        <p>Thanks,<br>The IXT Team</p>
